          .row
            .col-md-6
              .section-title
                h2.section-title__heading Our Clients

            .offset-md-1.col-md-5
              .section-title
                p.section-title__label We worked with
                p.section-title__desc Our favorite brands are our friends! We help them to achieve their goals, they help us to stay sharp.

